The paper is about automatic software repair, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The three repair methods discussed in the paper involve program synthesis (cs.PL), constraint-based search (cs.SY), and machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the correctness of generated patches, which is related to program verification (cs.CR).
